headline: First Western (MYFW) Tops Q1 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: First Western (MYFW) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 86.96% and 7.35%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
